title: Your phone at a glance
answer:
![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=112728) ![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=112729) ![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=112730) Y330 do not have the ambient light and proximity sensor and key backlight
![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=112731) Return Touch to return to the previous screen or exit the current application. When you are entering text, touch to hide the onscreen keyboard.
![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=112732) Home Touch to return to the home screen.
![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=112733) Menu Touch to display an option menu. Touch and hold this key to display the list of recently used applications.
